{"aid": "j0nzh1x46fe18j", "result": {"status": "active", "unique_views": 49, "request_instructor_me": false, "change_log": [{"type": "create", "anon": "no", "when": "2017-03-14T12:06:06Z", "data": "j09hrus63h56xc", "uid": "ie7xy8gtpwk1t5"}, {"type": "update", "anon": "no", "when": "2017-03-18T06:18:45Z", "data": "j0ev4kprnoko", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie"}, {"uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "type": "i_answer", "when": "2017-03-24T04:10:34Z", "to": "j09hrus4f76xb", "anon": "no", "data": "j0nb6u7x86e4nf"}], "upvote_ids": [], "id": "j09hrus4f76xb", "bookmarked": 5, "no_answer": 0, "i_edits": [], "is_bookmarked": false, "children": [{"folders": [], "is_tag_endorse": false, "created": "2017-03-24T04:10:34Z", "type": "i_answer", "tag_endorse_arr": [], "id": "j0nb6u7rv374ne", "bucket_name": "Today", "config": {}, "tag_endorse": [], "bucket_order": 2, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "children": [], "history": [{"content": "<p>请尝试分析下面的几个函数和宏&#xff1a;</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>mmu.h</p>\n<pre>#define PDX(la) ((((uintptr_t)(la)) &gt;&gt; PDXSHIFT) &amp; 0x3FF)<br />#define PTX(la) ((((uintptr_t)(la)) &gt;&gt; PTXSHIFT) &amp; 0x3FF)<br />#define PPN(la) (((uintptr_t)(la)) &gt;&gt; PTXSHIFT)<br />#define PGOFF(la) (((uintptr_t)(la)) &amp; 0xFFF)</pre>\n<p>glue_memlayout.h</p>\n<pre>#define VPT 0xFAC00000</pre>\n<p>pmm.c</p>\n<pre>void map_pgdir(pde_t * pgdir)</pre>\n<p>proc.c</p>\n<pre>static int setup_pgdir(struct mm_struct *mm)</pre>\n<p></p>", "anon": "no", "created": "2017-03-24T04:10:34Z", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "subject": ""}]}], "nr": 1008, "bucket_order": 2, "type": "question", "folders": ["lab2", "2017"], "no_answer_followup": 0, "num_favorites": 0, "bucket_name": "Today", "q_edits": [], "data": {"embed_links": []}, "request_instructor": 0, "tags": ["2017", "lab2", "student"], "created": "2017-03-14T12:06:06Z", "is_tag_good": false, "config": {}, "s_edits": [], "my_favorite": false, "default_anonymity": "no", "t": 1490369422072, "tag_good": [{"name": "Yong XIANG", "admin": true, "photo": null, "us": false, "id": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "class_sections": ["课程设计_i5j09fnsl7k5x0", "清华学生_i5j09fnsl7k5x0", "所有老师和助教_i5j09fnsl7k5x0"], "role": "instructor", "facebook_id": null, "email": "xyong@tsinghua.edu.cn", "admin_permission": 10}], "tag_good_arr": ["hdjonbiyfs62ie"], "history": [{"content": "<p>#查找页表</p>\n<p>cpu看到的都是线性地址&#xff0c;具体访存时放到总线上的地址是物理地址&#xff0c;在两者之间进行转换的是MMU&#xff0c;在MMU中通过查找页表项进行转换&#xff0c;过程如陈渝老师在视频中说的&#xff0c;也有对应的<a href=\"https://chyyuu.gitbooks.io/os_course_exercises/content/all/03-2-spoc-discussion.html\" target=\"_blank\">练习</a></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>#修改页表项</p>\n<p>要如何修改页表项呢&#xff1f;就跟普通的往内存里写数据一样&#xff0c;但是我们只知道页目录表的物理地址&#xff08;CR3中&#xff09;&#xff0c;不知道它的线性地址。</p>\n<p>在ucore中&#xff0c;页目录表的&#xff08;逻辑&#xff09;线性地址是0xFAC00000&#xff0c;即是说&#xff0c;MMU会用这个地址查找PDE中的表项&#xff0c;而其中的内容正是PDE的首地址的物理页号。</p>\n<p>那么问题来了&#xff0c;假如我要修改PDE中第&#43;2项&#xff0c;要给它哪个地址呢&#xff1f;是0xFAFCB002吗&#xff1f;&#xff08;查PDE两次回到自己&#xff0c;offset 2&#xff09;</p>\n<p>要修改PDE中第&#43;2项指向的页表的第&#43;3项呢&#xff1f;</p>", "anon": "no", "created": "2017-03-18T06:18:45Z", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "subject": "页机制中地址转换&#xff08;查找、修改&#xff09;"}, {"content": "<p>#查找页表</p>\n<p>cpu看到的都是线性地址&#xff0c;具体访存时放到总线上的地址是物理地址&#xff0c;在两者之间进行转换的是MMU&#xff0c;在MMU中通过查找页表项进行转换&#xff0c;过程如陈渝老师在视频中说的&#xff0c;也有对应的<a href=\"https://chyyuu.gitbooks.io/os_course_exercises/content/all/03-2-spoc-discussion.html\" target=\"_blank\">练习</a></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>#修改页表项</p>\n<p>要如何修改页表项呢&#xff1f;就跟普通的往内存里写数据一样&#xff0c;但是我们只知道页目录表的物理地址&#xff08;CR3中&#xff09;&#xff0c;不知道它的线性地址。</p>\n<p>在ucore中&#xff0c;页目录表的&#xff08;逻辑&#xff09;线性地址是0xFAC00000&#xff0c;即是说&#xff0c;MMU会用这个地址查找PDE中的表项&#xff0c;而其中的内容正是PDE的首地址的物理页号。</p>\n<p>那么问题来了&#xff0c;假如我要修改PDE中第&#43;2项&#xff0c;要给它哪个地址呢&#xff1f;是0xFAFCB002吗&#xff1f;&#xff08;查PDE两次回到自己&#xff0c;offset 2&#xff09;</p>\n<p>要修改PDE中第&#43;2项指向的页表的第&#43;3项呢&#xff1f;</p>", "anon": "no", "created": "2017-03-14T12:06:06Z", "uid": "ie7xy8gtpwk1t5", "subject": "页机制中地址转换&#xff08;查找、修改&#xff09;"}]}, "error": null}